Mr. Varun Malhotra will be in Kolkata tomorrow for The 'Capital Market Conclave' organised by ERIC-ICAI.

📈✨ Investing to secure our Financial Future is a journey worth embarking on. Check out these snapshots from the insightful event! 📸💼 #FinancialFuture #InvestingWisely #ShreeDelhiGujaratiSamaj #CommunityEngagement

Varun Malhotra will be in Bengaluru tomorrow for JITO's (Jain International Trade Organization) Session. Register here to attend:  https://jpfblr.org/events

Sending waves of gratitude to the Garden City! 🌆 Bengaluru, your warmth and enthusiasm were unmatched. 📚 Yesterday, we embarked on a journey to empower and educate at the Rajasthan Police Academy in Jaipur. 🚀 Our mission: Financial Literacy! 

A big thank you to Additional Director General of Police P. Raamjee, IPS, for giving us this opportunity 🙌 Sir, your dedication to enhancing financial awareness in the forces is truly commendable! 🌟

#FinancialLiteracy #RajasthanPoliceAcademy #Empowerment #Gratitude #PRAamjeeIPS

🎙️ Last month, our journey took us to the vibrant city of Kolkata, where I had the privilege of being a Speaker at an event organized by The Institute of Chartered Accountants of India 🌐

Together, we delved into the challenges and opportunities within the Indian Economy 🇮🇳

Being a part of discussions that shape our nation's economic landscape is truly inspiring.

My heartfelt thanks to #ICAI and Niraj Harodia Sir for the invaluable opportunity to share knowledge and insights. 🙏✨

 #ICAI #ChartingIndianEconomy #KnowledgeSharing #KolkataDiaries
